<emphasis bold="true" box="[1707,2000,2060,2097]" pageId="21" pageNumber="18">following locality</emphasis>
: CENTRAL 
<emphasis box="[1434,1587,2128,2158]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="18">AMERICA</emphasis>
: PANAMA: Volcan de 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1987,2106,2128,2158]" pageId="21" pageNumber="18">Chiriqui</emphasis>
(BMNH, MHNP).
</paragraph>
